<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Industries We Serve - Greymatter Accountancy</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/styles.css">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Sora:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header', { rootPath: '../', currentPage: 'page' }) %>

  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Industries We Serve</h1>
      <p>Deep expertise across London's diverse economy</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Industries Grid -->
  <section class="industries-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="industry-detail">
        <div class="industry-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-building"></i></div>
        <h2>Property & Construction</h2>
        <p>We understand the complexities of property accounting, from service charge management to development joint ventures.</p>
        <div class="industry-benefits">
          <span class="benefit"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Service charge accounting</span>
          <span class="benefit"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> CIS compliance</span>
          <span class="benefit"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Development project accounting</span>
          <span class="benefit"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Joint venture structuring</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="industry-detail">
        <div class="industry-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-gavel"></i></div>
        <h2>Professional Services</h2>
        <p>Law firms, consultants, and architects need accounting that understands billable hours, project costing, and partnership structures.</p>
        <div class="industry-benefits">
          <span class="benefit"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Billable hour accounting</span>
          <span class="benefit"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Partnership agreements</span>
          <span class="benefit"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> WIP management</span>
          <span class="benefit"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Fixed fee project accounting</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="industry-detail">
        <div class="industry-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-palette"></i></div>
        <h2>Creative & Media</h2>
        <p>From Shoreditch design studios to production companies, we speak the language of creative business accounting.</p>
        <div class="industry-benefits">
          <span class="benefit"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Project-based accounting</span>
          <span class="benefit"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Royalty tracking</span>
          <span class="benefit"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> IP asset management</span>
          <span class="benefit"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Tax relief eligibility</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="industry-detail">
        <div class="industry-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i></div>
        <h2>Retail & Hospitality</h2>
        <p>Multi-location businesses need robust accounting systems. We integrate with EPOS, manage payroll complexity, and track performance.</p>
        <div class="industry-benefits">
          <span class="benefit"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Multi-site accounting</span>
          <span class="benefit"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> EPOS integration</span>
          <span class="benefit"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Labour cost analysis</span>
          <span class="benefit"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Food & beverage cost control</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="industry-detail">
        <div class="industry-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-laptop-code"></i></div>
        <h2>Tech & Startups</h2>
        <p>Growing tech companies need accounting that supports fundraising, equity schemes, and fast growth. We get it.</p>
        <div class="industry-benefits">
          <span class="benefit"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> SEIS/EIS scheme compliance</span>
          <span class="benefit"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> R&D tax relief planning</span>
          <span class="benefit"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> ESOP and equity structuring</span>
          <span class="benefit"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Investor-ready reporting</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Is Your Industry Here?</h2>
      <p>Even if not listed, if you operate in London, we likely have experience in your sector. Let's talk.</p>
      <a href="../index.html#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Discuss Your Business</a>
    </div>
  </section>
  <%- include('partials/footer', { rootPath: '../', currentPage: 'page' }) %>
</body>
</html>
